{
  "texts": [
    "Each pair of dots represents the pair of sentences created with the same prompt.",
    "are overall slightly above those calculated based on the confusion matrix in Table 5.",
    "We included several other measurements in our experiment and hence conducted a second mixed-model logistic regression analysis to explore their relationships.",
    "We decided to include the length of the stimulus text as a fixed effect, since it was not possible to completely control this factor.",
    "The process we used to generate the stimuli is described in Section 2.3."
  ]
